Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是秀樹的好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是秀樹的好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.84,0:01:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，那個是好料的，我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，後面也發現有好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好料的散落一地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.78,0:01:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹快回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.72,0:01:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常大都在這時候是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.46,0:01:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來後要跟他說“歡迎回來”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來\N歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.33,0:02:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…大概完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明年又要重考了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.64,0:02:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#16         ちぃ，煮飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.52,0:02:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.42,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在補習班裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒什麼啦，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這種事跟ちぃ講也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，慘了\N連暑期輔導都開始了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.61,0:03:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，有電話，有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰打來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是主人打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.62,0:03:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快接起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，近來可好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你很快活嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我跟喜歡的人在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，都不知人家的辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？你好像不太順利是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事想問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績單差不多也該發了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.79,0:04:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.92,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子你已經拿到了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考得怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是E
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此？\N妳這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.24,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你平常都還可以\N可是一到考試成績就變差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是你的考運不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.28,0:04:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜\N因為只要你努力一定辦得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要參加下次的全國模擬考？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全國模擬考？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.13,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以當作考前的預演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.60,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能用來確認你現在的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還願意叫我老師啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.61,0:05:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒幫你做多少\N值得被你稱呼為老師的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會參加那個考試的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，那加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再打給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我要努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家看看我的潛力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.01,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果從K到N畫一條線A經過KT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩者的交會點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神來做早操吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手用力的往前舉起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一、二、三、四\N絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，今天不做早操\N三、二、三、四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.91,0:06:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要開始請假了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，因為快模擬考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以請了一個禮拜的假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很在意我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹打工要請假嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.62,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是會去接ちぃ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，今天就要開始苦讀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先去買個晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.88,0:07:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.51,0:07:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢包不見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.27,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才剛領的這一週的生活費啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.04,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下週領薪水前，要怎麼過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.36,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，都快模擬考了\N該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼讀得下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹又沒精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.78,0:08:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，成績往下掉\N連錢包也沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫“禍不單行”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ打工的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，路上小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天好像沒什麼精神耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.49,0:09:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看到秀樹沒精神\Nちぃ就會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹的錢包掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且因為成績下降\N所以在拼命用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過ちぃ卻什麼都幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ想幫秀樹做點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓他回復精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要有這份心\N做什麼本須和都會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，這是本週的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.89,0:10:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到薪水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.87,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給秀樹的話\N他一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？要把這個給我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.28,0:10:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣秀樹就會恢復精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.08,0:10:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這個我不能收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.13,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也有講過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是ちぃ工作賺來的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定要用在ちぃ想用的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.04,0:11:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的好意我心領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，用功，用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.90,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧，眼睛都充血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還…還好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.74,0:12:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道不要耍帥就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.15,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我們要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說薪水要ちぃ自己花用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ要用在秀樹身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.92,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要煮飯給秀樹吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.40,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前秀樹吃這裡\N咕嚕咕嚕做出來的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹一定會吃這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.07,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告！警告！瓦斯外洩了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快讓屋內保持通風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，是為了本須和啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ明明是為了秀樹去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹卻不收我的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ能為秀樹做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼事才能讓秀樹高興呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他每次看到好料的\N就會露出笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.43,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去買這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，有能讓他更高興的東西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.31,0:14:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，肚子餓到不能專心讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這股令人心動的香味是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.79,0:14:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去就完了\N我可是身無分文啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，不吃又讀不下書…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.94,0:14:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，肚子好餓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，找到馬鈴薯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯放進去了\N接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.59,0:14:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔、豬肉、洋蔥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對，就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.63,0:14:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了嗎？左手要縮起來\N別忘囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用刀時要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左手要縮起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉能幫我看熱水嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯還沒好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀\N飯沒煮好前不可以打開喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工請假還來借錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這麼好的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右轉轉，左轉轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我來試吃看看囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.64,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣秀樹就會高興了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會恢復精神嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最後還是唸不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.03,0:16:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣去參加模擬考\N真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錢，沒飯吃，又讀不下書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐她今天吃咖哩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.29,0:16:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，這股香味是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.15,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐教ちぃ跟絲茉茉做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.78,0:17:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹要ちぃ自己花用薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ就為秀樹煮了飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹最近都沒精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹沒精神的話\Nちぃ也會沒精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ想幫秀樹回復精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話來了，電話來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是主人打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保打來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，讀書順利嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我只是有點擔心你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，別講得好像我是第一次考試啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.59,0:18:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你進補習班頭一回考試時\N不是忘了寫名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式考試時要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.07,0:18:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一緊張\N就什麼都搞不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次我什麼都沒搞清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？到時候要靜下心來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.69,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？你幹嘛道歉啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒事沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝了，拜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？沒有…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左手要縮起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要仔細的撈出雜物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學到好多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐也說很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說秀樹也會很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹露出笑容\Nちぃ也會高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳穿那是什麼樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次在秀樹的\N好料的裡面看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹好像看得很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天絲茉茉也要這麼穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別穿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，拜託妳穿普通的衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.78,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…這樣不好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.26,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.93,0:20:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.83,0:20:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.80,0:20:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.73,0:20:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.98,0:20:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天考完後一起出門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.85,0:20:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉當然也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.09,0:20:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.12,0:20:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，這是學長的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.01,0:21:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.72,0:21:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.88,0:21:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.31,0:22:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.08,0:22:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.26,0:22:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
